Question 21:
Display current month calendar on screen ?
Command: cal
Description: cal command is used to print the current month calendar on screen

Question 22:
Display the hostname of your current server ?
Command: hostname
Description: hostname command is used to display the hostname of current machine

Question 23:
Display the current logged in username ?
Command: whoami
Description: whoami command is used to display the current logged in user

Question 24:
Ping "udemy.com" from your terminal ?
Command: ping -c5 udemy.com
Description: ping command is used to test connectivity, reachability.

Question 25:
Print recently triggered commands on your Linux system ?
Command: history
Description: history command is used to view the list of commands that user had triggered on the terminal
